description: This header file declares the exported API functions for the TLS Cipher Switch Object, including creation and initialization functions, specifically for the TLS implementation within the system.

methods.name: TlsCreateCipherSwitch
methods.description: Creates a new instance of the TLS Cipher Switch object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: TlsCsoCreate
methods.description: Creates a new TLS Cipher Switch Object with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: TlsCsoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes a given TLS Cipher Switch Object instance.
